line.words: Li di, §M konnen! Mwen ta renmen gen zèl!§ Epi menm kote a, de bèl zèl pouse sou do Emi. Li vole wo... piwo... e piwo ankò.. Epi li disparèt! Babay Emi!

subtitle.line: §I know!§ She says.§I wish I had wings!§ And sure enough, Amy grew two beautiful wings. She flew higher… and higher… and higher…and disappeared! Goodbye Amy!
